== Form Files ==

Each form is stored in its own sub-directory under <code>forms/</code>. The JSON file shares the name of the directory:

<pre>
forms/
└── Form1/
    ├── Form1.json       ← Form definition
    ├── Form1.bas        ← BASIC code for this form (optional)
    ├── Form1.js         ← JavaScript code for this form (optional)
    └── Elements/
        ├── Button1.json
        └── TextArea1.json
</pre>

