== Element Files ==

Each control (button, text box, label, etc.) on a form is stored as a separate JSON file in the <code>Elements/</code> sub-directory of the form.

The name of the element file must be unique to the project.
The same element name cannot be defined for two different forms. 
Element names cannot be form names. 
Names must be valid JavaScript variable names.

