|-
| <code>color</code> || String || Foreground / text colour (CSS value).
|-
| <code>backgroundColor</code> || String || Background colour (CSS value).
|-
| <code>fontFamily</code> || String || Font family (CSS value).
|-
| <code>fontSize</code> || String || Font size (CSS value, e.g. <code>"14px"</code>).
|-
| <code>fontStyle</code> || String || Font style: <code>"italic"</code>, <code>"normal"</code>, etc.
|-
| <code>fontWeight</code> || String || Font weight: <code>"bold"</code>, <code>"normal"</code>, etc.
